Comment: 10,0:04:23.49,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sybilladura Lelladybura!
Comment: 10,0:04:33.56,0:04:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this should get us there! {preference}
Comment: 10,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment, girls.
Comment: 10,0:04:40.22,0:04:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Metamorphie Vestesse! {crap, I can't remember if this was used before. I think it was}
