Comment: 10,0:05:01.08,0:05:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, thank you!
Comment: 10,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Be careful.
Comment: 10,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Comment: 10,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fired up!
Comment: 10,0:05:09.53,0:05:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Comment: 10,0:05:11.53,0:05:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 10,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tia Freyre!
Comment: 10,0:05:42.61,0:05:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're failures as teachers.
Comment: 10,0:05:45.98,0:05:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have a chance of making it.
Comment: 10,0:05:49.04,0:05:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko may be able to make something happen.
Comment: 10,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you expect a miracle.
Comment: 10,0:05:56.51,0:05:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko doesn't believe in miracles. However—
Comment: 10,0:05:59.83,0:06:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always believed in herself.
Comment: 10,0:06:19.64,0:06:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Faerie of wind, lend me your power!
Comment: 10,0:06:28.64,0:06:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is perfect! Jasminka, let it all out!
Comment: 10,0:06:42.58,0:06:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Jasminka!
Comment: 10,0:07:00.73,0:07:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Constanze!
Comment: 10,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1200)}It's all on you now!
Comment: 10,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can count on us!{## don't think she just means herself exclusively, she's part of the nine new witches now}
Comment: 10,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Amanda!
Comment: 10,0:07:27.23,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What—Who's broadcasting this?
Comment: 10,0:07:34.94,0:07:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that alert for?
Comment: 10,0:07:36.70,0:07:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a news flash about\Na missile launch or something.
Comment: 10,0:07:40.61,0:07:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A missile?! Are you serious?
Comment: 10,0:07:42.77,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Where's it coming from?
Comment: 10,0:07:45.36,0:07:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't even say where it's heading....
Comment: 10,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? What's going on?
Comment: 10,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this what it's talking about? {yes, as in the news flash}
Comment: 10,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting it too.
Comment: 10,0:07:54.79,0:07:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, this isn't a missile. {technically, it is}
Comment: 10,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those people?
Comment: 10,0:07:59.15,0:07:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,People?
Comment: 10,0:08:04.89,0:08:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the flying object's current location and trajectory.
Comment: 10,0:08:07.37,0:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heading for that country. {Japanese is the worst}
Comment: 10,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we intercept it?
Comment: 10,0:08:11.63,0:08:16.76,Default,,13,13,0,,Its speed is considerably slower than a common ballistic missile. There is a high probability of success.
Comment: 10,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be able to detect it any minute now.
Comment: 10,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you contacted the Prime Minister?
Comment: 10,0:08:22.45,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He is heading here now.
Comment: 10,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we should alert them?
Comment: 10,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do you intend to explain it?
Comment: 10,0:08:29.12,0:08:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That a mysterious missile just so happened to be fired from us at them?{## probably not "by us"}
Comment: 10,0:08:32.46,0:08:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the truth.
Comment: 10,0:08:35.49,0:08:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And you think they'll believe that explanation?
Comment: 10,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance. {minimizing of course}
Comment: 10,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This was an accident. {I know it's in the present, but they're speaking as if they'll explain it later}
Comment: 10,0:08:41.81,0:08:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it hits inside their territory,\Nwe bear no responsibility in the matter.
Comment: 10,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Comment: 10,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter the circumstances,\Nthey should be informed!
Comment: 10,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an imminent threat!
Comment: 10,0:08:53.17,0:08:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you intend to give them pretext for a counterstrike?
Comment: 10,0:08:57.61,0:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Comment: 10,0:08:58.88,0:09:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A separate bogey is in pursuit of the flying object. {spooky}
Comment: 10,0:09:01.76,0:09:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you certain?!
Comment: 10,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it an interceptor missile?
Comment: 10,0:09:06.76,0:09:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative. It appears to be smaller.
Comment: 10,0:09:09.47,0:09:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is it?!
Comment: 10,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Displaying on monitor.
Comment: 10,0:09:13.57,0:09:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Witches?
Comment: 10,0:09:16.51,0:09:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kagari?
Comment: 10,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, this is for Akko!
Comment: 10,0:09:23.87,0:09:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 10,0:09:24.45,0:09:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Comment: 10,0:09:29.25,0:09:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, faerie of fire!
Comment: 10,0:09:34.27,0:09:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pyro Booster!
Comment: 10,0:09:40.98,0:09:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, I was right!
Comment: 10,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Witches from Luna Nova!
Comment: 10,0:09:44.67,0:09:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is this in real time?
Comment: 10,0:09:46.10,0:09:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, who cares about witches? This isn't the time.
Comment: 10,0:09:51.06,0:09:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that they're trying to stop the missile?
Comment: 10,0:09:54.64,0:09:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Comment: 10,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it for us.
Comment: 10,0:10:02.63,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to you!
Comment: 10,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Akko!
Comment: 10,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lotte and Sucy!
Comment: 10,0:10:17.80,0:10:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The videos have spread so far there is no method to contain them.
Comment: 10,0:10:21.26,0:10:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you force them down?
Comment: 10,0:10:23.58,0:10:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,These leaks are unacceptable.
Comment: 10,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Comment: 10,0:10:30.04,0:10:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it.
Comment: 10,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We caught up!
Comment: 10,0:10:33.14,0:10:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... what?
Comment: 10,0:10:34.94,0:10:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, our magic is about to run out.
Comment: 10,0:10:38.48,0:10:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's like right there!
Comment: 10,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Missile evaded.
Comment: 10,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Number two, approaching!
Comment: 10,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Comment: 10,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?
Comment: 10,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen?
Comment: 10,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, what happened to those witches from before?
Comment: 10,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, the witches are still there!
Comment: 10,0:11:20.99,0:11:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You think witches can stop that thing?
Comment: 10,0:11:23.19,0:11:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno, but maybe there's something magic could do about it.
Comment: 10,0:11:25.92,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm gonna cheer them on!
Comment: 10,0:11:28.75,0:11:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in!
Comment: 10,0:11:29.76,0:11:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Comment: 10,0:11:30.65,0:11:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Us too!
Comment: 10,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Comment: 10,0:11:32.09,0:11:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Comment: 10,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Our magic is increasing.
Comment: 10,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why is that happening?
Comment: 10,0:11:47.83,0:11:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Comment: 10,0:11:48.86,0:11:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we should have no trouble flying now.
Comment: 10,0:11:54.22,0:11:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How can they remain flying?
Comment: 10,0:11:55.95,0:11:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Their magic shouldn't have lasted this long.
Comment: 10,0:12:02.31,0:12:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuel Spirit?
Comment: 10,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Comment: 10,0:12:06.64,0:12:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're speeding up. That light\Nis providing them with magic.
Comment: 10,0:12:10.71,0:12:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more lights appearing.
Comment: 10,0:12:13.42,0:12:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,People's thoughts are being relayed as magic without utilizing any sort of system.
Comment: 10,0:12:18.39,0:12:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! {Naruto Believe it!}
Comment: 10,0:12:20.41,0:12:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But those girls still believe.
Comment: 10,0:12:23.52,0:12:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They believe their actions can change\Npeople's feelings and surroundings.
Comment: 10,0:12:40.23,0:12:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm now streaming the video of Akko and Diana worldwide.
Comment: 10,0:12:43.89,0:12:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use a new method to show them witches\Nthe likes of which they've never seen before. {including what Chariot's about to do}
Comment: 10,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to the world!
Comment: 10,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Call for their support.
Comment: 10,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you great at working the mic?{## yolo, you said...}
Comment: 10,0:13:00.53,0:13:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please listen.
Comment: 10,0:13:03.03,0:13:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,These two witches are attempting\Nto stop a dangerous monster.
Comment: 10,0:13:08.27,0:13:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster is enormous and extremely powerful,
Comment: 10,0:13:11.69,0:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but they are fearlessly facing it head-on.
Comment: 10,0:13:15.40,0:13:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let them hear your support!
Comment: 10,0:13:18.84,0:13:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please believe in them!
Comment: 10,0:13:21.66,0:13:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That will become their power!
Comment: 10,0:13:25.18,0:13:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All of your believing hearts are truly...
Comment: 10,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Our magic!
Comment: 10,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn witches, always getting in our way!
Comment: 10,0:13:35.35,0:13:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut down all of the hijacked monitors!\NCancel all the TV broadcasts!
Comment: 10,0:13:39.86,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point trying to stop it now.{## "them" made me think of akko and diana, since he was calling them damn witches too, though he means the tv broadcasts}
Comment: 10,0:13:42.14,0:13:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,With how far this has spread, it cannot be unseen.{## typo if edit reverted}
Comment: 10,0:13:45.27,0:13:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What could witches possibly do?!\NNot to mention children!
Comment: 10,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell would have faith in them?!{## yeah i know but}
Comment: 10,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The people have already started to believe.
Comment: 10,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They simply wish to riot.
Comment: 10,0:14:00.39,0:14:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see that those witches are only worsening the uproar?
Comment: 10,0:14:04.66,0:14:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot!
Comment: 10,0:14:06.06,0:14:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Those girls are on the front line.
Comment: 10,0:14:08.98,0:14:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They are our greatest hope for stopping it!
Comment: 10,0:14:13.22,0:14:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be aiding them, not trying to interfere!
Comment: 10,0:14:16.38,0:14:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you believe in those witches?
Comment: 10,0:14:19.09,0:14:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe!
Comment: 10,0:14:23.22,0:14:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with him.
Comment: 10,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Prime Minister!
Comment: 10,0:14:28.20,0:14:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be watching over them right now.
Comment: 10,0:14:32.56,0:14:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to provide them with backup\Nin the event of their failure.
Comment: 10,0:14:37.78,0:14:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Comment: 10,0:14:39.98,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any objections?
Comment: 10,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Comment: 10,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let us watch them until the end.
Comment: 10,0:14:49.83,0:14:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Forget about dropping, our magic keeps going up and up!
Comment: 10,0:14:53.58,0:14:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll catch up in no time.
Comment: 10,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're there.
Comment: 10,0:14:56.94,0:14:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Comment: 10,0:14:58.01,0:15:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. Not until we stop it.
Comment: 10,0:15:06.94,0:15:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it looks like the Rod's power is maxed out!
Comment: 10,0:15:09.68,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You think we can use it to turn the missile into something harmless?
Comment: 10,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We will have to try.
Comment: 10,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go forth, Akko!
Comment: 10,0:15:27.37,0:15:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Metamorphie Faciesse!
Comment: 10,0:15:35.46,0:15:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Comment: 10,0:15:37.19,0:15:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab on!
Comment: 10,0:16:28.75,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
Comment: 10,0:16:36.23,0:16:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
Comment: 10,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
Comment: 10,0:17:01.92,0:17:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko?
Comment: 10,0:17:03.06,0:17:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice catch, me!
Comment: 10,0:17:05.66,0:17:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the legendary broom?
Comment: 10,0:17:07.90,0:17:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's what you'd call a dramatic reunion!
Comment: 10,0:17:22.61,0:17:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch me if you can!
Comment: 10,0:18:09.36,0:18:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Comment: 10,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yggdrasil.
Comment: 10,0:18:15.85,0:18:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Grand Triskelion.
Comment: 10,0:18:18.30,0:18:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can truly change the world,
Comment: 10,0:18:20.58,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make a world where everyone can smile with each other!{## "smile with each other"? sounds odd}{technically it should be at... but this kind of has a feeling of togetherness}
Comment: 10,0:18:25.14,0:18:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A believing heart is everyone's magic!
Comment: 10,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Noctu Orfei!
Comment: 10,0:18:38.85,0:18:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aude!
Comment: 10,0:18:44.00,0:18:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraetor!
Comment: 10,0:18:56.53,0:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\4a&HFF&\t(\fscx140\fscy140)}Shiny {\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\t(5606,5756,\1a&H00&\3a&H00&)}Arc! {do whatever you want here}{done}
Comment: 10,0:19:49.67,0:19:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She finally did it!
Comment: 10,0:19:52.55,0:19:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Andrew.
Comment: 10,0:19:55.36,0:19:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Father.
Comment: 10,0:19:56.34,0:20:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that I greatly misunderstood the witches.
Comment: 10,0:20:02.18,0:20:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you share your opinions on the value of witches with me?
Comment: 10,0:20:07.83,0:20:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, gladly!
Comment: 10,0:20:17.45,0:20:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart that believes in magic...
Comment: 10,0:20:20.95,0:20:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected that to be the origin of magic.
Comment: 10,0:20:23.72,0:20:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic was a far greater existence\Nthan I gave it credit for.
Comment: 10,0:20:28.74,0:20:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's well beyond the two of us.
Comment: 10,0:20:31.59,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And it will only continue to grow.
Comment: 10,0:20:55.20,0:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rod!
Comment: 10,0:21:02.12,0:21:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shiny Rod.
Comment: 10,0:21:16.16,0:21:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Comment: 10,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Croix.
Comment: 10,0:21:25.68,0:21:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Chariot.
Comment: 10,0:21:28.69,0:21:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmistress Holbrooke, I'm in your debt.
Comment: 10,0:21:31.31,0:21:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Croix, you'll always be welcome here.
Comment: 10,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 10,0:21:36.74,0:21:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's something I must accomplish after I clean up my messes.
Comment: 10,0:21:41.53,0:21:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you must accomplish?
Comment: 10,0:21:43.76,0:21:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 10,0:21:44.49,0:21:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to find a cure for Wagandea's curse before I return.
Comment: 10,0:21:49.47,0:21:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Croix...
Comment: 10,0:21:51.67,0:21:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Comment: 10,0:21:53.36,0:21:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine how it'd look if Akko learned how to fly while her teacher still can't.
Comment: 10,0:22:00.72,0:22:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tia Freyre.
Comment: 10,0:22:04.75,0:22:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Croix, I'll be waiting for you!
Comment: 10,0:22:09.36,0:22:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting...
Comment: 10,0:22:17.43,0:22:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind, check!
Comment: 10,0:22:18.68,0:22:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Broom, check!
Comment: 10,0:22:19.60,0:22:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Date, check!
Comment: 10,0:22:21.73,0:22:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's the May Fair, after all!
Comment: 10,0:22:26.98,0:22:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tia Freyre!
Comment: 10,0:22:33.63,0:22:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tia Freyre!
Comment: 10,0:22:34.96,0:22:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tia Freyre! Tia Freyre!
Comment: 10,0:22:40.84,0:22:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, it's too bad again.
Comment: 10,0:22:43.47,0:22:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But it felt like you almost had it.
Comment: 10,0:22:46.60,0:22:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Comment: 10,0:22:48.08,0:22:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're definitely progressing!
Comment: 10,0:22:50.73,0:22:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You think? Looked exactly the same as always to me.
Comment: 10,0:22:54.48,0:22:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what are you even here for\Nif you're not gonna cheer me on?
Comment: 10,0:23:00.86,0:23:07.40,Default,,13,13,0,,I came because of how confidently you invited me,\Nbut it appears we won't be seeing the decisive moment.
Comment: 10,0:23:08.70,0:23:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast! I feel like today's the day!
Comment: 10,0:23:11.66,0:23:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll make it today for sure!
Comment: 10,0:23:16.15,0:23:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Comment: 10,0:23:21.33,0:23:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko, you can do this. Your believing heart...
Comment: 10,0:23:24.78,0:23:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is magic, right?
Comment: 10,0:23:28.09,0:23:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 10,0:23:35.54,0:23:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
Comment: 10,0:23:42.31,0:23:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She flew.
Comment: 10,0:23:43.20,0:23:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
